room_title: Escape room "Mardi Gras Study" by Escape My Room in New Orleans
room_description: The year is 1990, and Odette DeLaporte has invited you to her study. The reclusive matriarch has not been seen in public for quite some time, yet she has agreed to meet with you with the hope that you can recover whatâ€™s been lost.
